query:
SELECT g.id as gestorId, g.userId, u.id as oderId, u.name, u.email
FROM gestores g
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE g.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT gestorId FROM relatorios_livres);
